```

## Enforcement

A `commit-msg` git hook in `scripts/commit-msg` automatically strips AI branding lines from commit messages. Install it after cloning:

```bash
cp scripts/commit-msg .git/hooks/commit-msg && chmod +x .git/hooks/commit-msg
```
